Yemen: Faith is Yemeni, peace among sheep","author":"Abu Amina Elias","date":"November 24, 2012","format":false,"excerpt":"Abu Huraira reported: The Messenger of Allah, peace and blessings be upon him, said, \u201cFaith is from Yemen and unbelief is from the east. Tranquility is found among people who tend to sheep. Pride and showing off are found among the uncivil owners of horses and camels.\u201d Source: S\u0323ah\u0323i\u0304h\u0323 Muslim\u2026","rel":"","context":"In &quot;Faith \u0627\u0644\u0627\u064a\u0645\u0627\u0646&quot;","block_context":{"text":"Faith \u0627\u0644\u0627\u064a\u0645\u0627\u0646","link":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/category\/faith-iman\/"},"img":{"alt_text":"","src":"","width":0,"height":0},"classes":[]},{"id":40703,"url":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/2023\/07\/07\/believers-endure-trials\/","url_meta":{"origin":40707,"position":1},"title":"Hadith on Faith: Believers endure trials, unlike hypocrites","author":"Abu Amina Elias","date":"July 7, 2023","format":false,"excerpt":"Ka\u2019b reported: The Prophet, peace and blessings be upon him, said, \u201cThe parable of the believer is that of a tender plant. The wind sways it at times, and it returns to balance at times. The parable of the hypocrite is that of a cedar tree. It continues to be\u2026","rel":"","context":"In &quot;Faith \u0627\u0644\u0627\u064a\u0645\u0627\u0646&quot;","block_context":{"text":"Faith \u0627\u0644\u0627\u064a\u0645\u0627\u0646","link":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/category\/faith-iman\/"},"img":{"alt_text":"","src":"","width":0,"height":0},"classes":[]},{"id":25039,"url":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/2017\/07\/10\/fitnah-flee-to-mountains\/","url_meta":{"origin":40707,"position":2},"title":"Hadith on Fitnah: Muslims flee to the mountains, escaping persecution","author":"Abu Amina Elias","date":"July 10, 2017","format":false,"excerpt":"Abu Sa\u2019id al-Khudri reported: The Messenger of Allah, peace and blessings be upon him, said, \u201cSoon the best property of a Muslim will be a flock of sheep he takes to the top of a mountain, or in the valleys of rainfall, fleeing with his religion from tribulations.\u201d Source: S\u0323ah\u0323i\u0304h\u0323\u2026","rel":"","context":"In &quot;Wisdom \u0627\u0644\u062d\u0643\u0645\u0629&quot;","block_context":{"text":"Wisdom \u0627\u0644\u062d\u0643\u0645\u0629","link":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/category\/wisdom-al-hikmah\/"},"img":{"alt_text":"","src":"","width":0,"height":0},"classes":[]},{"id":40664,"url":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/2023\/07\/05\/unbelievers-rigid\/","url_meta":{"origin":40707,"position":3},"title":"Hadith on Kufr: Unbelievers stay rigid until they break","author":"Abu Amina Elias","date":"July 5, 2023","format":false,"excerpt":"Jabir reported: The Messenger of Allah, peace and blessings be upon him, said, \u201cThe parable of the believer is that of a planted stalk. It stays rigid in one moment and bends down in another moment. The parable of the unbeliever is that of a cedar tree. It continues to\u2026","rel":"","context":"In &quot;Sin \u0627\u0644\u0625\u062b\u0645&quot;","block_context":{"text":"Sin \u0627\u0644\u0625\u062b\u0645","link":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/category\/sin-al-ithm\/"},"img":{"alt_text":"","src":"","width":0,"height":0},"classes":[]},{"id":2776,"url":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/2012\/04\/05\/ahl-al-kitab-hear-prophet\/","url_meta":{"origin":40707,"position":4},"title":"Hadith on Faith: People of the Book who hear of Muhammad","author":"Abu Amina Elias","date":"April 5, 2012","format":false,"excerpt":"Abu Huraira reported: The Messenger of Allah, peace and blessings be upon him, said, \u201cBy the One in whose hand is the soul of Muhammad, none from this nation of Jews and Christians hears of me, and then dies without having faith in my message, but t